Sentencas: The chemical composition of the cathode material influences the performance of the low temperature solid oxide fuel cells (SOFCs).
Titulo: Effect of cobalt and magnesium doping on the performance of Ba0.5Sr0.5Fe0.8O3 cathode for solid oxide fuel cell applications

Sentencas: In the present work, two different cathode materials (Ba0.5Sr0.5Co0.2Fe0.8O3 and Ba0.5Sr0.5Mg0.2Fe0.8O3) were prepared to assess the role of Mg in the place of Co on the performance of the SOFC.
Titulo: Effect of cobalt and magnesium doping on the performance of Ba0.5Sr0.5Fe0.8O3 cathode for solid oxide fuel cell applications

Sentencas: Symmetric cells were fabricated by using Gadolinium doped Cerium (GDC) electrolyte.
Titulo: Effect of cobalt and magnesium doping on the performance of Ba0.5Sr0.5Fe0.8O3 cathode for solid oxide fuel cell applications

Sentencas: From the X-ray diffraction analysis, the lattice parameter was measured as increased from 3.954 angstrom to 3.975 angstrom for the cathode with the presence of Mg compared with Co.
Titulo: Effect of cobalt and magnesium doping on the performance of Ba0.5Sr0.5Fe0.8O3 cathode for solid oxide fuel cell applications

Sentencas: On the other hand, Mg decreased the electric conductivity (35 +/- 1.6 S cm(-1)) compared with Co doping (56 +/- 2.4 S cm(-1)).
Titulo: Effect of cobalt and magnesium doping on the performance of Ba0.5Sr0.5Fe0.8O3 cathode for solid oxide fuel cell applications

Sentencas: Higher porosity (4.8%) was observed in the cathode material with Mg which resulted in more triple phase boundaries and promoted higher gas diffusion.
Titulo: Effect of cobalt and magnesium doping on the performance of Ba0.5Sr0.5Fe0.8O3 cathode for solid oxide fuel cell applications

Sentencas: Lower polarization resistance (R-P) values (7.95 and 1.07 Omega-cm(2)) were recorded at 600 degrees C and 700 degrees C respectively for the fuel cells fabricated with cathode having Mg compared with Co.
Titulo: Effect of cobalt and magnesium doping on the performance of Ba0.5Sr0.5Fe0.8O3 cathode for solid oxide fuel cell applications
